text: Sven-Olof Israelsson (born 13 May 1948) is a Swedish skier. He competed in the Nordic combined event at the 1972 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1948 births Category:Living people Category:Swedish male Nordic combined skiers Category:Olympic Nordic combined skiers of Sweden Category:Nordic combined skiers at the 1972 Winter Olympics Category:People from Dalarna
